{"tid":886810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"四川千人爭掘「太和玉」 專家指是鋪路石頭","createTime":"2018-11-02T11:44:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T13:17:01.000Z","uid":75969,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"be52a672ec5f0c5251ce8fc1786ae27a44da1332","tid":886810,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181102/_2018110219083178151.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181102%2F_2018110219083178151.jpg&h=8d55cead&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四川西昌日前流傳幾段「太和玉」影片，令當地太和鎮小麻柳村一個棄土場聚集近千人「尋寶」。可惜翌日（31日）便有玉石專家指出所謂「太和玉」，只是用作鋪路的石英石。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，最初發現石頭的是當地村民廖定清，及後請玉石愛好者鑑定，認為是一種前所未見的寶玉，更命名為「太和玉」。事件傳開後吸引過千民眾前來尋寶。<br />\n<br />\n西昌市國土資源局翌日發通告，指該處為棄土場區域，存在地質災害隱患，禁止民眾採挖，且未探明有玉石等重要礦產資源，呼籲民眾理性看待，勿信傳謠。而涼山州觀賞石寶玉石協會會長、國家觀賞石一級鑒評師熊峻松更「太和玉」是笑話，不過是大量石英石夾雜普通鵝卵石，價值僅限於鋪路用途。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181102/_2018110219083099915.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181102%2F_2018110219083099915.jpg&h=b20d04f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">專家指出「太和玉」只是鋪路用的石英石夾雜鵝卵石。 網圖<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181102/_2018110219083190424.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181102%2F_2018110219083190424.jpg&h=140f541f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">專家指出「太和玉」只是鋪路用的石英石夾雜鵝卵石。 網圖<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/855508\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F855508&d=TNc28JJvEqMuoJKdm3yFAhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=21459d05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F855508&h=44c6d636\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/855508</a>"},{"pid":"e2da7bd775b7567dc27b82dc4faf921b51cbad8d","tid":886810,"uid":75969,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:44:23.000Z","msg":"想玩鳩班支那人真係好易<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6637c4324156bf8adb595cc7f225bc495b7ee2d","tid":886810,"uid":21917,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:46:01.000Z","msg":"諗起當年玉靈芝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d45434f500cfe80717c104f03e3b81c148b0dd","tid":886810,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T12:11:06.000Z","msg":"成班文盲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上層仲有班奸官貪官<br />\n呢個國家無得救"},{"pid":"2db23ed8d90953dacbfed6dd738b7d9408b78723","tid":886810,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T12:41:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da4bdb760900f6adcef066adbf1e1c26c15e2509","tid":886810,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T12:42:11.000Z","msg":"食香港人屎可以防癌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29356f40ea4b7a7700aa7da12797c98f86bc4515","tid":886810,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T12:47:30.000Z","msg":"習近平見到咁樣，就決定嚴刑治國"},{"pid":"34e0a6a6ef7057de5f6715b451797f2e7c8a214e","tid":886810,"uid":143269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da4bdb760900f6adcef066adbf1e1c26c15e2509","tid":886810,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T12:42:11.000Z","msg":"食香港人屎可以防癌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T12: